{"tid":1770743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗128之外我哋仲有一個好重要既地方要去","createTime":"2019-12-05T11:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T11:19:47.000Z","uid":186363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df8e47dda15c84b8a7742296ec7ca71846d8ac58","tid":1770743,"uid":186363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"係英國領事館啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n有一班人係英領想留守到十三號嘅原因<br />\n係因為英國大選就係個日完結<br />\n係英國嘅戰友同某政黨有協議<br />\n如果呢段期間英國領事館前坐滿人，大選後就會回應香港人道危機以及中國違反中英聯合聲明等議題<br />\n<br />\n所以你哋每一個都好重要<br />\n多一個都好有意義<br />\n希望如果可以就去英領嗰度留守啦<br />\n我明依幾日天氣好凍<br />\n唔係個個都頂得順<br />\n但人哋都講到咁明<br />\n我地連百幾人既位都坐唔滿<br />\n仲講咩爭取民主自由<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6549134bff2785fac083979f1008aba9e4d36e8a","tid":1770743,"uid":186363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"4f9571fad4ec9f890665db81d15b5d417716fc3d","tid":1770743,"uid":186363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"fd55ba9bcad3de81824ae8f64e621e82aeba5237","tid":1770743,"uid":186363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"5cf760d80b847d4b94b3a21efb3eeb5f9e6c198d","tid":1770743,"uid":186363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"成日叫人哋廢國<br />\n人哋宜家開到聲唔係唔行動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb854e211800a53dbcaa2c049e7a027da0570332","tid":1770743,"uid":186363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"c4413afaa71584f7dc3a9c9a676ed3c5adc314f7","tid":1770743,"ui